. # Migration steps
The concept of 'position' has been removed from the schema. Instead there is a now a 'groupBy' field, which should contain the list of property names that should be used as aggregation keys.
There is are also 2 new fields, visibilityProperty and timestampProperty, that defines which properties are for visibility and timestamp.
Migration for accumulo positions
The following changes may need to be made to your schema files:
- Remove any reference to positions
- Any properties that were previously stored in the column qualifier need to be added to the groupBy properties list - in the order that they are currently stored.
- If you used the visibility position for a property, then this property name should be assigned to the visibilityProperty field.
- If you used the timestamp position for a property, then this property name should be assigned to the timestampProperty field.
Example schema migration
If your schema was previously:
``` json
{
    "entities": {
        "BasicEdge": {
            "vertex": "vertex",
            "properties": {
                "prop1a": "keyed-string",
                "prop1b": "keyed-string",
                "prop2": "simple-string",
                "visibility": "visibility.string",
                "timestamp": "timestamp.long",
            }
        }
    },
"types": {
    "vertex": {
        "class": "java.lang.String"
    },
    "keyed-string": {
        "class": "java.lang.String",
        "position": "COLUMN_QUALIFIER"
    },
    "string": {
        "class": "java.lang.String",
        "position": "VALUE"
    },
    "visibility.string": {
        "class": "java.lang.String",
        "position": "VISIBILITY"
    },
    "timestamp.long": {
        "class": "java.lang.Long",
        "position": "TIMESTAMP"
    }
},

 "vertexSerialiserClass": "gaffer.serialisation.simple.StringSerialiser"

}
```
This would need to be migrated to:
``` json
{
    "entities": {
        "BasicEdge": {
            "vertex": "string",
            "properties": {
                "prop1a": "string",
                "prop1b": "string",
                "prop2": "string",
                "visibility": "string",
                "timestamp": "long"
            },
            "groupBy": [
                "prop1a", "prop1b"
            ]
        }
    },
"types": {
    "vertex": {
        "class": "java.lang.String"
    },
    "string": {
        "class": "java.lang.String"
    },
    "long": {
        "class": "java.lang.Long",
    }
},

"vertexSerialiserClass": "gaffer.serialisation.simple.StringSerialiser",
"visibilityProperty": "visibility",
"timestampProperty": "timestamp"

}
```
