. ## Migration Steps
The summarise flag has been replaced with a groupBy property in the view on each edge/entity.
The groupBy in the view allows you to define a subset of the the groupBy properties in the schema. If you don’t specify a groupBy in the view then it will use what is in the schema.
So to migrate from previous summarise true/false values:
summarise = false           ->   don’t specify a groupBy  (groupBy null)
summarise = true            ->   set groupBy to an empty array for each entity/edge
new partial summarise   ->   specify some properties in the groupBy
