Some quick notes:
 * An Entity is RELATED to an EntityId if the Entity's vertex is equal to the EntityId vertex
 * An Entity is RELATED to an EdgeId if either the Entity's vertex is equal to either the EdgeId's source or destination
 * An Edge is RELATED to an EntityId if either the Edge's source or destination matches the EntityId's vertex
 * An Edge is RELATED to an EdgeId if the Edge's source, destination and directed values are equal to the EdgeId. Note that the EdgeId directed value could be EITHER, this will mean Edges that are DIRECTED OR UNDIRECTED will be matched.
